The Telegraph - Calcutta
 Hair promoted
London: The ICC elevated three new umpires  Darrell Hair and Simon Taufel of Australia and New Zealands Billy Bowden to its Elite Panel. The trios performances in the recently concluded World Cup in South Africa sealed their rise to the top tier, ICC chief executive Malcolm Speed said.  (AFP)  Copyright 
